SELECT 'CreateSalesOrderScheduleLine' || '::' || "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID" AS "ID",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID"                                     AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine",
       "SalesOrder"."ID"                                         AS "SalesOrder",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreationTime"                           AS "Time",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreatedBy_ID"                           AS "ExecutedBy",
       "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreationExecutionType"                  AS "ExecutionType"
FROM (SELECT "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID" AS ID,
             "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."SalesOrder_ID" AS "Header_ID",
             "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreationTime" AS "CreationTime",
             "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreatedBy_ID" AS "CreatedBy_ID",
             "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreationExecutionType" AS "CreationExecutionType"
      FROM "o_custom_SalesOrderScheduleLine" AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
      ORDER BY "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."ID") AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
         LEFT JOIN "o_custom_SalesOrder" AS "SalesOrder"
                   ON "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."Header_ID" = "SalesOrder"."ID"
WHERE "SalesOrderScheduleLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
